## Hooks

# Collapse threads by default, and jump to the last message
#folder-hook . push "<collapse-all>*"

# Display sent-mail folders differently
folder-hook sent-mail 'set index_format="%2N %3C %Z %[%b %d %H:%M] - %-22.22t (%3l) %s"'

send-hook       .       'my_hdr Reply-To: Gregory SACRE <gsa@softkinetic.com>'
